The group also said that following the undertaking of more than 5,000 actions to ask the United Kingdom to improve the nutrition of mothers and children, the government announced the funding of a project, The Power of Nutrition, which will benefit 5 million women and children through nutritional interventions.
In response to one of the most frequently asked questions on its website, "what makes you think it is possible to end extreme poverty?"
Global Citizen said: "The way to do this will be long and difficult, sometimes we will fall and fail.
